data.description: Price Drop!! Seller says sell!!WOW!!!Location, location, location, walk or bike to the quaint waterside town of Safety Harbor! This rarely available 2nd floor, Harbour Towne condo with an elevator is gorgeous! Builder updated 2 bedroom 2 bath condo overlooking Tampa Bay in a beautiful eleven (11) acre low-density community of mature oaks and beautiful palms is relaxing and quiet. Centrally located to Tampa and St. Pete Airports and all major connecting roads. Amenities include a clubhouse, pool, fitness center, two tennis courts, car wash, and BBQ area. This lovely unit has new polished porcelain floors, new Alside double-hung lifetime warranty windows, a Trane air condition system, S/S appliances, an inside laundry hook-up, an enclosed balcony, a walk-in closet and so much more, you just have to see. Walking and biking trails are literally outside your front door. The boat launch at Phillippe park and Safety Harbor marina are just minutes away. Kayaking, biking, shops, restaurants, entertainment, museums, cultural center, art/music festivals and so much more are right at your fingertips. Great for a vacation get-a-way, full-time residence, or investment property. The possibilities are limitless.
